message: "If you use this software in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Kurt"
    given-names: "Orhan Nedim"
title: "tcga-gdc-downloader"
abstract: "A command-line and graphical tool to download TCGA RNA-seq gene expression 
  count data from the NCI GDC portal, assemble a gene x sample count matrix, and 
  annotate samples with GDC clinical data and PanCanAtlas CDR survival and subtype 
  annotations."
version: "2.1.1"
date-released: "2026-02-28"
url: "https://github.com/onedimkurt/tcga-gdc-downloader"
repository-code: "https://github.com/onedimkurt/tcga-gdc-downloader"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - TCGA
  - GDC
  - RNA-seq
  - bioinformatics
  - genomics
  - cancer
  - gene expression
  - pan-cancer
references:
